<plot>A superpatriotic 1950's youth, rejected for military service due to having every conceivable medical disqualification, is recruited by Senator Joe McCarthy to become America's defender against the Red Menace, Hoverboy! Whether Hoverboy fights the Rosenbergs, or an innocent scientist with a powerful robot, he stays true to his boss' motto, "There's no time to think!," even as he causes more havoc than he stops.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?247862</url></doc>
